 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>잘 안되었던것</h3>\n<p>공통로그인 체크가 필요한 부분에선 loginCheck를 true로 바꿔줘야 하는데, 그 부분이 강의에서 빠져있어서 조금 헤맸다…</p>\n<h3 id=\"해결법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"해결법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>해결법</h3>\n<p>RequestConfig라는 어노테이션을 이렇게 만들었을때,</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Target</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">ElementType</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>METHOD<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Retention</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">RetentionPolicy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>RUNTIME<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@Documented</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@interface</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">RequestConfig</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">boolean</span> <span class=\"token function\">loginCheck</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>로그인 체크가 필요한(loginCheck를 true로 만들) 메소드 위에 이렇게 작성해준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token annotation punctuation\">@RequestConfig</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>loginCheck <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"배운것느낀점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%B0%EC%9A%B4%EA%B2%83%EB%8A%90%EB%82%80%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"배운것느낀점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>배운것/느낀점</h3>\n<p>백엔드 서버개발을 할 때 파일업로드, restapi 인증정보, 각종 설정값들이 많은데 @Value 어노테이션으로도 사용할 수 있지만, GlobalConfig 클래스롤 만들어서 한곳에서 관리를 해서 사용하니 확장성이 좋았던것 같다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"[8일차]SpringBoot 기반으로 서버 개발하기-8","date":"April 27, 2022"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Inflearn/[8일차]SpringBoot 기반으로 서버 개발하기-8/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/DB/[MariaDB] SQL 에러들 + 해결방법/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[MariaDB] SQL 에러들 + 해결방법"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2486386679","3128451518"]}